                                                                                                    3.1 PREPARE

                                                                                                                                                 Purpose
                                                                                                        The purpose of the Prepare step is to carry out essential activities at the organization,
                                                                                                        mission and business process, and information system levels of the organization to
                                                                                                        help prepare the organization to manage its security and privacy risks using the Risk
This publication is available free of charge from: https://doi.org/10.6028/NIST.SP.800-37r2




                                                                                                        Management Framework.



                                                                                                    PREPARE TASKS—ORGANIZATION LEVEL
                                                                                                    Table 1 provides a summary of tasks and expected outcomes for the RMF Prepare
                                                                                                    step at the organization level. Applicable Cybersecurity Framework constructs are also
                                                                                                    provided.
                                                                                                                       TABLE 1: PREPARE TASKS AND OUTCOMES—ORGANIZATION LEVEL

                                                                                                                     Tasks                                          Outcomes
                                                                                                     TASK P-1                              • Individuals are identified and assigned key roles for
                                                                                                     RISK MANAGEMENT ROLES                   executing the Risk Management Framework.
                                                                                                                                             [Cybersecurity Framework: ID.AM-6; ID.GV-2]
                                                                                                     TASK P-2                              • A risk management strategy for the organization that
                                                                                                     RISK MANAGEMENT STRATEGY                includes a determination and expression of organizational
                                                                                                                                             risk tolerance is established.
                                                                                                                                             [Cybersecurity Framework: ID.RM; ID.SC]
                                                                                                     TASK P-3                              • An organization-wide risk assessment is completed or an
                                                                                                     RISK ASSESSMENT—ORGANIZATION            existing risk assessment is updated.
                                                                                                                                             [Cybersecurity Framework: ID.RA; ID.SC-2]
                                                                                                     TASK P-4                              • Organizationally-tailored control baselines and/or
                                                                                                     ORGANIZATIONALLY-TAILORED CONTROL       Cybersecurity Framework Profiles are established and
                                                                                                     BASELINES AND CYBERSECURITY             made available.
                                                                                                     FRAMEWORK PROFILES (OPTIONAL)           [Cybersecurity Framework: Profile]
                                                                                                     TASK P-5                              • Common controls that are available for inheritance by
                                                                                                     COMMON CONTROL IDENTIFICATION           organizational systems are identified, documented, and
                                                                                                                                             published.
                                                                                                     TASK P-6                              • A prioritization of organizational systems with the same
                                                                                                     IMPACT-LEVEL PRIORITIZATION             impact level is conducted.
                                                                                                     (OPTIONAL)                              [Cybersecurity Framework: ID.AM-5]
                                                                                                     TASK P-7                              • An organization-wide strategy for monitoring control
                                                                                                     CONTINUOUS MONITORING STRATEGY—         effectiveness is developed and implemented.
                                                                                                     ORGANIZATION                            [Cybersecurity Framework: DE.CM; ID.SC-4]



